dc_title_s: Open space and center designation map: Middle Township, New Jersey
dc_description_s: This is part of a collection of maps of Middle Township that are to be used along with the Environmental Resource Inventory of Middle. The maps focus upon zoning, open space & government owned parcels, center designations, and taxes.|Project Number: 4182|Scale: 1:24000|Prepared for the Township of Middle with a grant from the Department of Environmental Protection, Office of Environmental Services.|Drawn by L. B. Landgraf|One of four maps belonging to the Environmental Resource Inventory: Middle Township (Phase II).
